places.bin.gz is compiled from GeoNames data.

  Source:  https://download.geonames.org/export/dump/ (cities1000,
           admin1CodesASCII, countryInfo)
  License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)
           https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
  Credit:  "This work is based on data from GeoNames (www.geonames.org)."

Rebuild with `node apps/worker/scripts/build-geo-index.mjs`, which pins the
sha256 of every input file into the artifact's header.

Attribution is also required where the derived place labels are shown to
users — see the credit in the web app's help modal, not just this file.
